response.summary:
Mechatronic Engineer from National University of Colombia, with extensive experience as a program-
mer in multiple languages, platforms and operating systems, with fast learning to work in newest
development platforms. I am characterized by logical reasoning to solve complex problems, proactive,
responsible, and committed to ethical and moral principles that allow me to work as a team.

I have experience leading development teams in web platform design and implementation projects, as
well as in migration from monolithic architectures to decoupled architectures based on microservices.

I also have experience developing projects that involve the design, prototyping, and construction
of automated devices, both for data detection, measurement, and acquisition systems; and for
servo-controlled mechanisms (Hardware and Software).
